WEBVTT

00:02.330 --> 00:03.661
PREVIOUSLY ON "SALEM"...

00:03.700 --> 00:04.997
Cotton: RITUM MAGNI.

00:05.030 --> 00:06.133
John: THE GRAND RITE?

00:06.170 --> 00:07.296
Cotton:
IT SAYS THIS OBJECT,

00:07.340 --> 00:08.739
THIS "MALUM,"

00:08.770 --> 00:10.203
IS THOUGHT TO BE PRESENT

00:10.240 --> 00:11.502
AT EVERY GRAND RITE
THROUGHOUT HISTORY.

00:11.540 --> 00:14.008
THIS OBJECT IS EVIL.

00:14.040 --> 00:16.349
IT CONSECRATES THE EARTH
FOR THE DEVIL'S RETURN.

00:16.380 --> 00:18.848
John: IT WAS HERE FOR DELIVERY.
SOMEONE WAS EXPECTING IT.

00:18.880 --> 00:20.541
Mary: SO THE OTHERS
HAVE TURNED ON ME.

00:20.580 --> 00:21.512
Titu ba: YES.

00:21.550 --> 00:22.710
EACH AND EVERY ONE.

00:22.750 --> 00:23.819
Mary: ROSE?

00:23.850 --> 00:25.181
Titu ba: EVERYONE.

00:25.220 --> 00:27.654
IF YOU WISH
FOR JOHN ALDEN TO LIVE,

00:27.690 --> 00:29.829
YOU WILL COMPLETE
THE GRAND RITE.

00:29.860 --> 00:31.327
Cotton:
WHAT IS THE GRAND RITE?

00:31.360 --> 00:33.191
Rose: [ GURGLING ]

00:35.430 --> 00:38.991
YOU THINK
YOU CAN DANGLE ME LIKE A PUPPET?

00:39.030 --> 00:42.761
YOU'RE THE PUPPETS,
ALL OF YOU -- PUPPETS!

00:42.810 --> 00:44.334
John: I THOUGHT YOU SAID

00:44.370 --> 00:45.667
SATURN WOULD COMPEL HER
TO SPEAK THE TRUTH.

00:45.710 --> 00:47.007
Cotton: IT DID.

00:47.040 --> 00:48.871
SOMETIMES
THE TRUTH IS A RIDDLE.

00:48.910 --> 00:50.502
John: AND THE ANSWER?

00:50.550 --> 00:52.313
Cotton: I MUST THINK
AND THEN THINK AGAIN.

00:55.650 --> 00:56.878
Anne: FATHER?

00:56.920 --> 00:58.581
[ GASPS ]

00:58.620 --> 00:59.951
AAH!

00:59.990 --> 01:01.287
Mrs. Hale: COME, CHILD.

01:01.320 --> 01:04.027
IT'S TIME WE TALKED
ABOUT YOUR FATHER.

01:04.060 --> 01:07.427
Mary: YOU BROUGHT THE MALUM
TO SALEM BEHIND MY BACK.

01:20.440 --> 01:21.702
[ RAT SQUEAKING ]

01:21.740 --> 01:23.446
[ PEOPLE COUGHING ]

01:35.120 --> 01:38.419
Captain:
NOT ONE OF THEM WILL SURVIVE.

01:38.460 --> 01:42.396
NOR THE REST OF US,
AT THIS RATE.

01:42.430 --> 01:45.490
10 DAYS BECALMED.

01:45.530 --> 01:48.135
NEARLY OUT OF FOOD AND WATER.

01:48.170 --> 01:52.539
WE'VE NO HOPE
UNLESS WE CATCH THE WIND.

01:54.280 --> 01:59.070
Grim Man: IT IS NOT THE WIND
THAT WE MUST CATCH, CAPTAIN.

01:59.110 --> 02:00.771
IT IS A WITCH.

02:00.820 --> 02:04.483
GIRL, LOOK AT ME.

02:04.520 --> 02:08.581
Captain: WE HAVE SEARCHED EVERY
PASSENGER AND CREW MEMBER

02:08.620 --> 02:11.589
FOR YOUR SUPPOSED WITCHES.

02:11.630 --> 02:13.120
NONE WERE FOUND.

02:13.160 --> 02:16.323
Grim Man:
THERE IS A WITCH ON THIS SHIP.

02:18.170 --> 02:22.630
YOU UNDERSTAND ME, CAPTAIN?

02:22.670 --> 02:27.278
THE WITCH WILL KILL EVERYONE
ABOARD IN ORDER TO STOP ME.

02:27.310 --> 02:29.608
WE WILL FIND THE WITCH.

02:29.650 --> 02:31.072
[ COUGHING CONTINUES ]

02:34.820 --> 02:36.685
Mary: MAKE NO MISTAKE.

02:36.720 --> 02:39.109
IT COULD JUST AS WELL
BE YOUR HEAD.

02:39.150 --> 02:42.278
ROSE BROUGHT THE MALUM HERE
BEHIND MY BACK

02:42.330 --> 02:45.128
TO COMPLETE THE GRAND RITE
WITHOUT ME.

02:45.160 --> 02:48.152
WHOSE IDEA WAS IT TO TURN
THE PURITANS' HATRED

02:48.200 --> 02:49.462
AGAINST THEMSELVES?

02:49.500 --> 02:50.990
TO USE THEM TO ACHIEVE

02:51.030 --> 02:53.339
THE FIRST GRAND RITE
IN CENTURIES?

02:53.370 --> 02:56.567
WHO MADE THAT POSSIBLE?

02:56.610 --> 02:58.498
ME.

02:58.540 --> 03:02.749
YET YOU AND THAT FOUL BITCH
MISTRUSTED ME.

03:02.780 --> 03:06.568
AND MUCH WORSE FOR YOU,
YOU UNDERESTIMATED ME.

03:06.620 --> 03:08.815
Mr. Hale:
BUT KILLING THE SAMHAIN,

03:08.850 --> 03:11.410
DO YOU HAVE ANY IDEA
WHAT YOU'VE DONE?

03:11.450 --> 03:14.317
Mary: THE QUESTION

03:14.360 --> 03:17.750
IS NOT WHETHER I UNDERSTAND
WHAT I HAVE DONE,

03:17.790 --> 03:21.419
BUT WHETHER YOU UNDERSTAND
WHAT YOU MUST NOW DO.

03:24.700 --> 03:27.692
Mr. Hale: I DO.

03:27.740 --> 03:31.699
YOU HAVE CLAIMED
THE ANCIENT RIGHT.

03:31.740 --> 03:35.278
I RECOGNIZE YOU
AS THE NEW SAMHAIN.

03:46.960 --> 03:51.249
I WILL HONOR AND OBEY
YOUR POWER, EARNED IN BLOOD,

03:51.290 --> 03:54.999
AND SHARE THE WORD WITH THE REST
OF THE HIVE.

03:58.130 --> 04:01.793
Mary: FULL HUNTER'S MOON
IS SOON UPON US.

04:01.840 --> 04:03.637
WE NEED EIGHT MORE DEAD BY THEN.

04:03.670 --> 04:08.437
AND I HAVE A PLAN...

04:08.480 --> 04:13.645
TO PUT US WITHIN REACH OF
OUR GOAL WITH ONE SINGLE MOVE.

04:13.680 --> 04:16.979
THREE SACRIFICED ALL AT ONCE.

04:17.020 --> 04:18.885
BUT MARK ME WELL --

04:18.920 --> 04:24.278
IF ANYONE GOES BEHIND MY BACK,
I HOLD YOU RESPONSIBLE.

04:24.330 --> 04:26.082
YOU WILL PAY FOR IT,

04:26.130 --> 04:28.496
OR YOUR WIFE
AND SWEET DAUGHTER WILL.

04:31.370 --> 04:32.997
[ "CUPID CARRIES A GUN" PLAYS ]

04:39.010 --> 04:41.729
* POUND ME THE WITCH DRUMS

04:41.780 --> 04:43.338
* WITCH DRUMS

04:43.380 --> 04:45.974
* POUND ME THE WITCH DRUMS

04:47.220 --> 04:49.814
* POUND ME THE WITCH DRUMS

04:49.850 --> 04:51.249
* THE WITCH DRUMS

04:51.290 --> 04:53.815
* BETTER PRAY FOR HELL

04:53.860 --> 04:59.150
* NOT HALLELUJAH

05:17.410 --> 05:19.674
[ INSECTS CHIRPING ]

05:19.720 --> 05:22.041
Anne: A SPY?

05:24.090 --> 05:27.309
WHAT DO YOU MEAN?

05:27.360 --> 05:29.180
IS HE WORKING FOR THE FRENCH?

05:29.220 --> 05:30.528
Mrs. Hale: NO!
[ SCOFFS ]

05:30.560 --> 05:33.120
OF COURSE NOT.

05:33.160 --> 05:34.525
[ SIGHS ]

05:34.560 --> 05:37.199
I SHOULD HAVE SAID NOTHING.

05:37.230 --> 05:41.394
BUT YOUR INFERNAL SNOOPING
ONLY ENDANGERS US ALL.

05:41.440 --> 05:45.900
YOUR FATHER
IS A CONFIDENTIAL AGENT.

05:45.940 --> 05:48.477
HE MAKES VERY OCCASIONAL REPORTS

05:48.510 --> 05:50.546
TO AGENTS REPRESENTING
ANOTHER FOREIGN POWER.

05:50.580 --> 05:52.639
Anne:
THEN WHO? AND WHY?

05:52.680 --> 05:56.741
Mrs. Hale: WHAT DOES IT MA'I'I'ER
TO WHOM YOUR FATHER SPEAKS?

05:56.790 --> 05:59.418
IT'S JUST POLITICS, DEAR.

05:59.460 --> 06:00.757
OF NO IMPORT.

06:00.790 --> 06:02.257
Anne: NO IMPORT?

06:02.290 --> 06:06.056
THAT MY FATHER IS A TRAITOR
IS OF NO IMPORT?!

06:06.800 --> 06:08.028
Mrs. Hale: NEVER SAY THAT.

06:08.060 --> 06:09.391
YOUR FATHER IS NOT A TRAITOR.

06:09.430 --> 06:11.898
HE IS A MAN
OF THE HIGHEST IDEALS!

06:11.930 --> 06:15.764
EVERYTHING YOUR FATHER DOES,
HE DOES FOR YOU.

06:15.800 --> 06:20.601
KEEP OUT OF HIS AFFAIRS
FOR YOUR OWN GOOD.

06:20.640 --> 06:24.246
Anne: I AM U'I'I'ERLY UNCONVINCED
BY YOUR STORY, MOTHER.

06:24.280 --> 06:27.943
HE SEEMED TO VANISH
BEFORE MY EYES.

06:27.980 --> 06:30.346
I MAKE NO APOLOGIES.

06:30.390 --> 06:34.451
AND I CHOOSE TO WALK THROUGH
LIFE WITH MY EYES OPEN.

06:34.490 --> 06:36.879
UNLIKE YOU.

06:36.930 --> 06:42.869
Mrs. Hale: I KNOW YOU THINK ME A
STUPID WOMAN WITH NO CURIOSITY,

06:42.900 --> 06:44.959
BUT YOU DON'T UNDERSTAND.

06:48.170 --> 06:51.264
THE PROBLEM WITH KNOWING THINGS

06:51.310 --> 06:54.074
IS THAT YOU CAN NEVER
UNKNOW THEM.

06:56.480 --> 06:58.607
[ INDISTINCT CONVERSATIONS ]

07:21.370 --> 07:24.100
Mab: HAS IT ARRIVED?

07:24.140 --> 07:27.109
Mr. Hale: PATIENCE.

07:30.280 --> 07:32.271
THIS...

07:37.020 --> 07:39.580
...MESSAGE I'VE BEEN WAITING FOR
FROM THE SHIP.

07:39.620 --> 07:41.918
WINDSTILLE.

07:41.960 --> 07:44.087
"WE ARE BECALMED.

07:44.130 --> 07:47.349
HE SEARCHES,
BUT I REMAIN HIDDEN."

07:47.400 --> 07:50.164
IF THEY FAIL TO HOLD HIM,

07:50.200 --> 07:52.998
HE COULD ARRIVE AT ANY TIME.

07:53.040 --> 07:55.429
Mab: HAVE YOU WARNED
MARY SIBLEY?

07:55.470 --> 07:57.358
Mr. Hale: NO.

07:57.410 --> 07:59.037
SHE KNOWS NOTHING OF THE GERMANS

07:59.070 --> 08:00.435
NOR OF MY CONTACT WITH THEM

08:00.480 --> 08:02.334
NOR OF THE IMPENDING THREAT.

08:02.380 --> 08:05.975
IF THEY SUCCEED
IN KEEPING HIM AT BAY,

08:06.010 --> 08:08.478
THEN SHE HAS NO NEED TO KNOW.

08:08.520 --> 08:10.784
AND IF HE CANNOT BE STOPPED,

08:10.820 --> 08:13.618
WELL, THEN IT'S AN ENTIRELY
NEW GAME, ISN'T IT?

08:13.660 --> 08:16.458
Mab: IT THREATENS EVERYTHING.
SHOULDN'T YOU TELL HER?

08:16.490 --> 08:17.957
Mr. Hale:
KNOWLEDGE IS POWER.

08:17.990 --> 08:21.050
AND WITH REGARD TO POWER,

08:21.100 --> 08:23.967
SHE HAS MORE THAN HER SHARE
AT THE MOMENT,

08:24.000 --> 08:26.093
WOULDN'T YOU AGREE?

08:28.070 --> 08:30.664
Tituba: ARE YOU SURE
YOU'VE DONE THE RIGHT THING?

08:30.710 --> 08:33.178
Mary: WERE YOU SURE
WHEN YOU BROUGHT ME IN?

08:33.210 --> 08:34.529
Titu ba: YES.

08:34.580 --> 08:36.332
I SAVED YOUR LIFE.

08:36.380 --> 08:38.143
AND I WILL NEVER CEASE
SAVING IT.

08:38.180 --> 08:40.876
Mary: I KNOW.

08:40.920 --> 08:42.217
COME.

08:50.530 --> 08:52.589
I MUST FIND THE MALUM.

08:52.630 --> 08:54.052
Tituba:
JOHN ALDEN HAS IT.

08:54.100 --> 08:55.590
Mary: YES.

08:55.630 --> 08:58.519
AND HE KNOWS HE HAS
SOMETHING OF POWER,

08:58.570 --> 09:01.596
SOMETHING WITCHES WOULD KILL
AND DIE FOR.

09:01.640 --> 09:03.107
HE WILL HAVE WELL-HIDDEN IT.

09:03.140 --> 09:05.005
Tituba: WELL, THEN
HOW WILL YOU FIND IT?

09:05.040 --> 09:08.339
Mary: I'VE A MIND
TO SEARCH HIS MIND.

09:08.380 --> 09:11.099
Titu ba: DREI\AC|3â€™I WALKING?

09:11.150 --> 09:12.549
THERE HAS TO BE ANOTHER WAY.

09:12.580 --> 09:14.116
Mary: WE'RE RUNNING
OUT OF TIME, TITUBA.

09:14.150 --> 09:16.516
WITHOUT THE MALUM
AND ALL IT CONTAINS,

09:16.550 --> 09:18.211
OUR GRAND RITE IS NOT POSSIBLE.

09:18.250 --> 09:19.615
TRUST ME.

09:19.660 --> 09:21.616
ONCE INSIDE,
I'LL FIND THE MALUM,

09:21.660 --> 09:22.581
AND THEN I'LL GET OUT.

09:22.630 --> 09:23.927
Tituba: INSIDE?

09:23.960 --> 09:26.349
IT IS NOT A HOUSE YOU INVADE
BUT A MAN!

09:26.390 --> 09:28.597
AND NOT JUST ANY MAN.

09:28.630 --> 09:32.122
ARE YOU SURE IT IS THE MALUM YOU
SEEK AND NOT JUST ACCESS TO HIM?

09:32.170 --> 09:33.762
Mary: [ SCOFFS ]

09:33.800 --> 09:35.961
WHATEVER MY PERSONAL FEELINGS
ARE FOR JOHN,

09:36.000 --> 09:37.365
I AM ONLY SEEKING THE MALUM.

09:37.410 --> 09:39.037
Tituba:
DO YOU HAVE ANY IDEA

09:39.070 --> 09:40.879
WHAT CRAWLING AROUND
INSIDE HIS DREAMS

09:40.910 --> 09:42.377
COULD DO TO YOU AND TO HIM?

09:42.410 --> 09:45.277
IT COULD LEAVE EITHER
OR BOTH OF YOU SHATI'ERED,

09:45.310 --> 09:47.574
UNABLE TO TELL DREAMS
FROM REALITY.

09:47.620 --> 09:49.144
YOU COULD BE LOST, TRAPPED!

09:49.180 --> 09:53.310
THERE ARE OTHER WAYS
TO FIND THE MALUM.

09:53.360 --> 09:55.817
I CANNOT LIE.
I AM AFRAID.

09:55.860 --> 09:56.952
Mary: GOOD.

09:56.990 --> 09:58.287
BE AFRAID.

09:58.330 --> 09:59.991
WATCH OVER ME.

10:00.030 --> 10:02.157
BUT THIS IS MY CHOICE.

10:02.200 --> 10:05.897
I WILL DO THIS
WITH OR WITHOUT YOU.

10:05.930 --> 10:08.933
TITUBA, SEND ME. NOW.

10:11.610 --> 10:14.135
Tituba: [ SIGHS ]

10:30.460 --> 10:33.623
GO NOW.
CATCH A FALLING STAR.

10:33.660 --> 10:36.629
GET WITH CHILD A MANDRAKE ROOT.

10:36.670 --> 10:39.366
TRAVEL BACK
WHERE PAST YEARS ARE.

10:39.400 --> 10:42.198
THROUGH THE CLOVEN DEVIL'S HOOF.

10:42.240 --> 10:44.936
WHAT YOU SEEK IS IN HIS HEART.

10:44.970 --> 10:47.438
KNOW HIS THOUGHTS
THROUGH ANGEL'S ART.

10:47.480 --> 10:49.971
AS TORCHES EVER READY BE,

10:50.010 --> 10:53.468
THROUGH DAYLIGHT'S GATE
STEP ONE, TWO, THREE.

11:24.080 --> 11:28.676
Mary: [ Distorted ]
WHY HAVE YOU WAITED SO LONG?

11:28.720 --> 11:31.587
[ MOANING ]

11:42.530 --> 11:43.929
John: [ GASPS ]

11:49.870 --> 11:52.771
Mary: [ EXHALES SHARPLY ]

11:52.810 --> 11:55.779
Tituba:
ENJOYING YOURSELF?

11:55.810 --> 11:58.074
Mary:
I DIDN'T FIND IT YET.

12:00.750 --> 12:03.082
BUT I KNOW I CAN.

12:07.820 --> 12:09.412
John: [ EXHALES ]

12:22.100 --> 12:24.068
Grim Man:
THIS SEA IS UNNATURAL.

12:24.110 --> 12:25.407
I SMELL IT. I FEEL IT.

12:25.440 --> 12:27.305
WE ARE UNDER A DARK ENCHANTMENT.

12:27.340 --> 12:30.275
Captain: WE HAVE SEARCHED
HIGH AND LOW.

12:30.310 --> 12:32.449
THERE IS NO WITCH ON THIS SHIP!

12:32.480 --> 12:35.074
Grim Man:
AND I SAY THERE IS.

12:35.120 --> 12:37.088
Captain:
WE HAVE SEARCHED EVERYONE.

12:37.120 --> 12:40.385
TWICE.
SO WHERE IS THE WITCH?

12:40.420 --> 12:42.479
Grim Man: RIGHT HERE.

12:42.520 --> 12:46.422
Captain: AAAH!

12:46.460 --> 12:49.725
Grim Man:
WHERE IS THE KNOT, CAPTAIN?

12:49.760 --> 12:51.489
Captain: [ SPITS ]

12:57.710 --> 12:59.598
Grim Man: WHERE HAVE YOU
HIDDEN THE KNOT?

12:59.640 --> 13:01.904
[ BONES CRACK ]

13:01.940 --> 13:05.774
WHERE IS THE KNOT
THAT BINDS THE WIND?

13:05.810 --> 13:09.177
Captain:
FRIB SCHEIBE UND STIRB!

13:09.220 --> 13:15.750
SIE WERDEN DIE NEUE WELT
NIE LEBEND ERRIECHEN!

13:15.790 --> 13:18.281
[ GROANS ]

13:20.000 --> 13:23.492
MY NECK!

13:23.530 --> 13:26.124
AROUND MY NECK!

13:28.470 --> 13:29.789
[ SHING! ]

13:33.510 --> 13:35.899
Grim Man: AUF WIEDERSEHEN.

13:38.150 --> 13:39.913
[ GULLS CRYING ]

13:42.480 --> 13:43.640
Boatswain:
CAPTAIN, THE WIND'S UP.

13:43.690 --> 13:45.339
THE SAILS ARE FULL.

13:47.320 --> 13:50.050
Grim Man: IAM NOW MASTER
OF THIS SHIP.

13:53.200 --> 13:57.796
TELL THE HELMSMAN DUE WEST.

13:57.830 --> 14:00.663
Mercy: CLOSE YOUR EYES...

14:00.700 --> 14:03.464
AND YOU BREAK AN EGG.

14:03.510 --> 14:05.660
AND YOU IMAGINE YOUR WEDDING,

14:05.710 --> 14:08.508
SO YOU'RE STANDING THERE
IN FRONT OF THE MEETING HOUSE

14:08.540 --> 14:10.303
HOLDING A BUNCH OF FLOWERS.

14:10.350 --> 14:12.170
THE BELLS ARE RINGING FOR YOU.

14:12.210 --> 14:14.314
AND THEN WHEN YOU OPEN
YOUR EYES,

14:14.350 --> 14:16.818
YOU SEE THE FACE OF THE MAN
YOU'RE TO MARRY.

14:16.850 --> 14:21.514
Emily: BUT WE ALREADY KNOW
WHO DOLLIE'LL MARRY.

14:21.560 --> 14:24.529
STINKY, OLD JOE BARKER.

14:24.560 --> 14:25.982
Dollie: I WILL NOT.

14:26.030 --> 14:27.520
Emily: BUT -- BUT YOU'VE ALREADY
BUNDLED WITH HIM.

14:27.560 --> 14:28.595
Dollie: HAVE NOT.

14:28.630 --> 14:29.756
Emily:
BUT YOU'RE GOING TO.

14:29.800 --> 14:31.859
Dollie: YES.

14:31.900 --> 14:33.891
TONIGHT.

14:33.940 --> 14:35.931
THERE'S GOT TO BE SOMEONE ELSE
FOR ME.

14:35.970 --> 14:37.369
Mercy:
WELL, IF THERE IS,

14:37.410 --> 14:39.435
THE VENUS GLASS
WILL SHOW HIM TO YOU.

14:39.470 --> 14:40.903
Dollie:
[ CHUCKLES LIGHTLY]

14:40.940 --> 14:42.635
Mercy: BUT FIRST YOU HAVE TO
DRINK THE TEA.

14:46.580 --> 14:48.116
ALL OF IT.

14:54.260 --> 14:56.478
Dollie: [ CHUCKLES ]

15:28.460 --> 15:30.280
[ SCREAMS ]

15:30.330 --> 15:31.888
[ WATER SIZZLES ]

15:31.930 --> 15:34.922
[ WHIMPERING ]

15:34.960 --> 15:35.927
DID YOU SEE THAT?

15:35.960 --> 15:37.427
Emily:
WHAT DID YOU SEE?

15:37.470 --> 15:39.062
DID YOU SEE JOE BARKER?

15:39.100 --> 15:42.160
Dollie: NO, I...

15:42.200 --> 15:44.509
I DON'T KNOW WHAT I SAW, BUT...

15:44.540 --> 15:47.236
I...

15:47.280 --> 15:48.679
BUT I -- BUT I HAVE TO GO NOW.

15:48.710 --> 15:52.009
UM, I'LL -- I'LL BE LATE
FOR MY BUNDLING,

15:52.050 --> 15:53.779
AND MY MOTHER WILL BEAT ME

15:53.820 --> 15:57.017
FOR RUINING
A PERFECT LY FINE MATCH.

15:57.050 --> 15:59.018
Emily:
WE ALL SHOULD GO, TOO.

16:07.300 --> 16:09.757
Emily:
[ BREATHES DEEPLY ]

16:09.800 --> 16:10.698
I DID IT.

16:10.730 --> 16:12.425
AND IT WORKED JUST --

16:12.470 --> 16:14.688
JUST LIKE YOU SAID IT WOULD.

16:14.740 --> 16:16.332
I-I GAVE HER THE POTION FIRST,

16:16.370 --> 16:18.338
AND THEN I PICTURED IT
IN MY MIND,

16:18.370 --> 16:20.201
AND SHE SAW IT.

16:20.240 --> 16:23.209
Mary: AND THIS IS JUST
THE BEGINNING.

16:23.250 --> 16:27.209
NEXT YOU WILL HELP PUSH SALEM
OVER THE EDGE,

16:27.250 --> 16:28.615
BUT FIRST...

16:28.650 --> 16:32.211
YOU MUST LEARN TO WALK
WHEREVER YOU WILL

16:32.250 --> 16:35.481
WITHOUT YOUR BODY.

16:48.270 --> 16:53.628
Cotton: I BEGGED TO SEE
YOUR FACE, LORD.

16:53.680 --> 16:57.878
AM I LOOKING AT IT NOW?

16:57.910 --> 16:59.969
John: THEY SAY IT'S THE FIRST
SIGN OF FOLLY,

17:00.010 --> 17:01.147
TALKING TO ONESELF.

17:01.180 --> 17:04.980
Cotton: I WASN'T TALKING
TO MYSELF.

17:05.020 --> 17:08.012
BUT TO GOD.

17:08.060 --> 17:11.848
OR MY FATHER.

17:11.890 --> 17:13.391
IF THERE IS A DIFFERENCE.

17:13.430 --> 17:14.988
John: IS HE HERE?

17:15.030 --> 17:17.919
Cotton: WORSE.

17:17.970 --> 17:19.562
HERE.

17:19.600 --> 17:22.694
John: I THINK WE'RE NOT
SO DIFFERENT.

17:22.740 --> 17:24.105
Cotton: [ CHUCKLES ]

17:24.140 --> 17:25.869
THAT WOULD WORRY ME IMMENSELY

17:25.910 --> 17:29.277
WERE I NOT ALREADY CONSUMED
WITH OTHER WORRIES.

17:38.990 --> 17:44.257
AND APPARENTLY THERE ARE SOME
TRUTHS NOT CONTAINED IN BOOKS.

17:44.290 --> 17:47.726
KNOWLEDGE MUST BE TESTED

17:47.760 --> 17:52.368
AGAINST THE ANVIL OF EXPERIENCE.

17:52.400 --> 17:55.528
LAST NIGHT MY KNOWLEDGE CRACKED
LIKE POORLY FORGED STEEL.

17:55.570 --> 17:57.367
AFI'ER WHAT THAT WITCH SAID,

17:57.410 --> 18:00.129
I CAN BE SURE OF NOTHING
BUT MY DOUBTS.

18:00.180 --> 18:01.932
I DOUBT EVERYTHING.

18:01.980 --> 18:06.644
MY BOOKS, MY TOOLS, MY METHODS.

18:06.680 --> 18:09.478
EVEN MYSELF.

18:09.520 --> 18:12.387
John: THEN YOU FIGHT
WITH THE WEAPONS YOU HAVE.

18:12.420 --> 18:13.887
Cotton: MEANING?

18:13.920 --> 18:16.252
John:
IF ALL YOU HAVE IS DOUBT,

18:16.290 --> 18:19.054
THEN YOU MAKE DOUBT ITSELF
THE WEAPON.

18:19.090 --> 18:22.992
YOU QUESTION EVERYTHING.

18:23.030 --> 18:25.726
Cotton: EVEN MYSELF?

18:25.770 --> 18:28.568
John:
ESPECIALLY YOURSELF.

18:28.600 --> 18:31.603
Cotton: I DO BELIEVE GOD BROUGHT
US TOGETHER FOR A REASON.

18:31.640 --> 18:33.938
John:
TO DRIVE EACH OTHER INSANE?

18:33.980 --> 18:38.098
Cotton: NO.

18:38.150 --> 18:40.175
'CAUSE THE SHADOW OVER SALEM
REQUIRES MORE LIGHT

18:40.220 --> 18:41.869
THAN EITHER OF US
CAN PROVIDE ALONE.

18:47.220 --> 18:51.919
John: YOU KNOW MORE
THAN ANYONE ABOUT...

18:51.960 --> 18:53.655
WELL, EVERYTHING.

18:56.160 --> 18:59.789
SO WHAT DO YOU KNOW
ABOUT DREAMS?

18:59.830 --> 19:02.663
Cotton: [ Whispering ]
THE UNDISCOVERED COUNTRY.

19:04.570 --> 19:05.867
Cotton: DREAMS.

19:05.910 --> 19:08.003
[ Normal voice ]
MOST MEN DISMISS THEM.

19:08.040 --> 19:09.974
BUT BY MY CALCULATION,

19:10.010 --> 19:13.719
A MAN WHO LIVES HIS FULL
BIBLICAL SPAN OF 70 YEARS

19:13.750 --> 19:18.187
WILL SPEND AS MANY AS 20 OF THEM
IN ANOTHER REALM,

19:18.220 --> 19:19.642
WHERE NOTHING IS AS IT SEEMS.

19:19.690 --> 19:21.487
John: SO YOU BELIEVE
THEY'RE REAL?

19:21.520 --> 19:23.226
Cotton: THEY ARE.

19:23.260 --> 19:25.683
OUR OWN PRIVATE AMERICA,

19:25.730 --> 19:29.621
A NEW WORLD FILLED WITH EQUAL
PARTS TERROR AND DELIGHT.

19:29.660 --> 19:34.290
APPARENTLY ONE NOT NEED BE
A HOUSE TO BE HAUNTED.

19:34.340 --> 19:36.638
John: WHAT DO YOU MEAN?

19:36.670 --> 19:39.833
Cotton: YOU'RE NOT THE ONLY ONE
WHO KNOWS WHAT IT FEELS LIKE

19:39.870 --> 19:42.338
TO HOLD DESIRES THAT COME TRUE
ONLY IN DREAMS.

19:42.380 --> 19:45.804
BUT EVERY MORNING,
WE HAVE A CHOICE.

19:45.850 --> 19:48.375
FORGET OUR DREAMS...

19:48.420 --> 19:50.547
OR LIVE THEM.

19:52.720 --> 19:54.984
Mrs. Barker: MY MOTHER
SEWED MR. BARKER AND ME

19:55.020 --> 19:58.683
INTO THIS BAG WHEN I WAS A GIRL.

19:58.730 --> 20:01.722
SUCH PLEASANT NIGHTS WE SPENT
TALKING OF THIS AND THAT.

20:01.760 --> 20:04.866
THAT STITCH KEEPS YOU
FROM HAVING TOO MUCH PLEASURE

20:04.900 --> 20:06.390
BEFORE THE WEDDING NIGHT.

20:06.430 --> 20:08.034
NOTHING BELOW THE WAIST.

20:13.910 --> 20:17.539
Joe: IS IT TRUE YOU'VE BEEN
IN THE HOUSE OF SEVEN GABLES?

20:17.580 --> 20:20.174
Dollie: OH, YES.
MANY TIMES.

20:20.210 --> 20:22.576
MY FRIEND MARCY LIVES THERE NOW.

20:22.620 --> 20:24.838
Joe: AREN'T YOU AFRAID
TO BE CLOSE TO HER?

20:24.890 --> 20:26.778
Dollie: NO.

20:28.390 --> 20:31.086
Joe: ARE YOU AFRAID
TO BE CLOSE TO ME?

20:42.140 --> 20:43.061
[ GASPS ]

20:44.610 --> 20:47.977
[ SCREAMING ]

20:52.610 --> 20:54.316
Mrs. Barker: WICKED GIRL!

20:54.350 --> 20:57.046
THAT BAG'S SEEN THREE
GENERATIONS MARRIED!

20:57.080 --> 20:58.445
THIS ISN'T OVER, LI'I'I'LE MISSY!

20:58.490 --> 21:00.981
I'LL TAKE THIS UP
WITH YOUR MOTHER!

21:22.940 --> 21:25.909
Mary:
WHERE IS IT, MY LOVE?

21:25.950 --> 21:28.441
SHOW ME WHERE IT IS.

21:30.790 --> 21:33.315
John:
H DON'T UNDERSTAND.

21:33.360 --> 21:34.418
Mary: NO?

21:34.460 --> 21:35.688
John: NO.

21:35.720 --> 21:37.324
WHAT DOES THIS MEAN?

21:37.360 --> 21:39.453
Mary: DO YOU CARE?

21:39.490 --> 21:41.299
IT IS.

21:41.330 --> 21:43.252
WE ARE.

21:43.300 --> 21:44.494
THAT'S ALL THAT MATTERS.

21:55.680 --> 21:58.240
REAL ENOUGH FOR YOU?

22:02.650 --> 22:04.345
OR THIS?

22:07.050 --> 22:08.688
I NEED TO KNOW WHERE IT IS.

22:08.720 --> 22:10.051
John: WHAT?

22:20.200 --> 22:22.668
Mary: [ PANTING ]

22:29.240 --> 22:31.140
I FOUND THE MALUM.

22:31.180 --> 22:33.148
IT'S IN COREY'S GRAVE.

22:33.180 --> 22:36.479
ALDEN HAS HIDDEN IT
IN COREY'S GRAVE.

22:36.520 --> 22:38.010
Tituba: I WARNED YOU.

22:38.050 --> 22:40.848
DREAM WALKING IN ANY MAN
IS DANGEROUS,

22:40.890 --> 22:41.982
LET ALONE ONE THAT YOU LOVE.

22:42.020 --> 22:43.658
Mary: [ SCOFFS ]

22:43.690 --> 22:46.079
Tituba: YOU COULD LOSE YOUR WAY
AND NEVER COME BACK.

22:46.130 --> 22:48.894
KEEP OUT OF THAT MAN'S HEAD.

23:19.790 --> 23:22.793
Mrs. Barker: LITI'LE BITCH TORE
MY GREAT-GRAN'S BUNDLING BAG.

23:22.830 --> 23:24.969
Mrs. Trask: AND YOUR
STINK-BREATHED BOY

23:25.000 --> 23:26.922
POKED A HOLE
IN YOUR PRECIOUS BAG,

23:26.970 --> 23:28.437
TRIED TO POKE ONE IN MY GIRL!

23:28.470 --> 23:30.199
Mrs. Barker: THERE'S NO HOLES
IN THAT BAG

23:30.240 --> 23:31.798
BUT THE ONES SHE TORE
RUNNING OUT.

23:31.840 --> 23:33.933
Mrs. Trask: AND WHO'D BELIEVE
YOU OR ANY BARKER?

23:33.980 --> 23:36.938
Mary: [ Whispering ] SEE,
MY DEAR? IT'S WORKING.

23:36.980 --> 23:38.607
Mrs. Trask: EVERYONE KNOWS
YOU'RE A PACK OF LIARS

23:38.650 --> 23:40.277
AND CHEATS GETTING RICH
OFF THE REST OF US.

23:40.310 --> 23:42.642
Mrs. Barker: YOU STOP TALKING
FILTH ABOUT MY FAMILY

23:42.680 --> 23:43.908
OR I'LL STOP YOU TALKING.

23:45.820 --> 23:47.458
Dollie: [ LAUGHS ]

23:47.490 --> 23:49.708
Mrs. Trask: WHAT ARE YOU
LAUGHING AT, YOU LITI'LE MINX?!

23:49.760 --> 23:52.786
THOSE BARKERS MAY BE A FOUL LOT,

23:52.830 --> 23:54.320
BUT THEY HAVE MONEY ENOUGH,

23:54.360 --> 23:56.089
AND IT WAS A FINE MATCH
FOR THE LIKES OF YOU,

23:56.130 --> 23:58.325
AND YOU HAD TO RUIN IT
WITH YOUR SILLY IDEAS.

24:01.170 --> 24:03.502
Mercy: [ INHALES SHARPLY ]

24:18.490 --> 24:20.185
Anne: CAPTAIN ALDEN,

24:20.220 --> 24:22.688
WHERE ARE YOU OFF TO
WITH SUCH URGENCY?

24:22.720 --> 24:25.086
John: NOWHERE.

24:25.130 --> 24:28.099
JUST...TAKING IN THE AIR.

24:28.130 --> 24:30.598
Anne: OH, I UNDERSTAND
COMPLETELY.

24:30.630 --> 24:32.598
YOU'RE NOT A MAN
USED TO TOWN LIFE.

24:32.630 --> 24:36.464
YOUR BODY PROBABLY LONGS
FOR THE WILDERNESS.

24:43.480 --> 24:45.471
CAPTAIN?

24:45.510 --> 24:49.879
John: I'M SORRY. I...

24:49.920 --> 24:52.388
I DON'T KNOW WHAT OVERCAME ME.

24:52.420 --> 24:53.853
PLEASE EXCUSE ME.

25:01.730 --> 25:04.961
Mab: CAPTAIN ALDEN.
AN HONOR --

25:05.000 --> 25:07.366
AND I HOPE A PLEASURE
TO SEE YOU.

25:07.400 --> 25:08.958
ANYONE TAKE YOUR FANCY?

25:09.000 --> 25:11.560
John: YES.
I NEED AT LEAST THREE.

25:11.610 --> 25:12.736
[ WOMEN CHUCKLE ]

25:28.690 --> 25:31.386
Mary: CLEVER GIRL.

25:31.430 --> 25:33.523
THANKS TO WHAT YOU MADE
DOLLIE SEE,

25:33.560 --> 25:38.668
THE TOWN IS MORE THAN HALFWAY TO
SEEING THE BARKERS AS WITCHES.

25:38.700 --> 25:41.760
NOW ONE SPARK
WILL LIGHT THE FIRE.

25:43.300 --> 25:47.009
YOU REMEMBER ALL I TOLD YOU?

25:47.040 --> 25:48.837
Mercy: YES.

25:48.880 --> 25:51.041
BUT WILL IT REALLY WORK?

25:51.080 --> 25:53.344
HOW WILL I LEAVE MY BODY?

25:53.380 --> 25:55.678
Mary: FOLLOW YOUR BLISS.

25:55.720 --> 25:59.019
IT WILL LEAD YOU
OUT OF YOUR BODY

25:59.050 --> 26:01.189
AND OUT OF THE WINDOW.

26:01.220 --> 26:05.179
STAY FOCUSED AND REMEMBER,

26:05.230 --> 26:09.223
YOUR JOB TONIGHT
IS TO TERRIFY MRS. TRASK.

26:09.260 --> 26:10.921
MAKE HER SEE MRS. BARKER.

26:10.970 --> 26:14.736
SHE MUST TELL EVERYONE SHE WAS
ATI'ACKED BY MRS. BARKER.

26:14.770 --> 26:16.533
Mercy: I UNDERSTAND.

26:16.570 --> 26:18.936
ARE YOU GONNA SEND ME NOW?

26:24.450 --> 26:26.702
Mary: CLOSE YOUR EYES.

26:26.750 --> 26:30.242
PICTURE WHERE YOU WANT TO GO.

27:03.790 --> 27:05.519
Mrs. Trask: [ GASPS ]

27:05.550 --> 27:06.619
[ EXHALES SHARPLY ]

27:06.650 --> 27:07.787
DOLLIE?

27:07.820 --> 27:10.015
[ SIGHS ] DAMN.

27:10.060 --> 27:12.255
IF YOU DON'T LEARN TO CONTROL
YOUR DAMN CAT,

27:12.290 --> 27:13.325
I'LL SKIN IT MYSELF.

27:21.570 --> 27:23.800
[ GASPS ]

27:26.010 --> 27:28.171
[ SHUDDERING ]

27:51.700 --> 27:53.565
[ INSECTS CHIRPING ]

28:09.080 --> 28:11.389
John:
THIS IS BUT A DREAM.

28:14.090 --> 28:17.753
Mary: LIFE ITSELF
MIGHT BE BUT A DREAM.

28:17.790 --> 28:20.054
WHY NOT ENJOY IT?

28:28.270 --> 28:33.207
Anne: TRY TO REMAIN STILL,
CAPTAIN ALDEN.

28:33.240 --> 28:34.400
Mary:
WHAT ARE YOU DOING HERE?

28:34.440 --> 28:37.603
Anne:
LEARNING THE WONDERS

28:37.640 --> 28:38.902
OF GOD'S OWN CREATION.

28:47.320 --> 28:49.083
Mary: JOHN?

28:49.120 --> 28:53.352
[ Echoing ]
WHERE ARE YOU, JOHN?

28:53.390 --> 28:55.790
[ MEN YELLING IN DISTANCE ]

28:55.830 --> 28:56.899
Mary:
[ BREATHING HEAVILY]

28:59.470 --> 29:02.769
[ YELLING IN DISTANCE
CONTINUES ]

29:09.680 --> 29:11.307
Titu ba: MARY!

29:18.420 --> 29:19.648
MARY!

29:19.690 --> 29:20.987
MARY, COME OUT NOW!

29:30.200 --> 29:30.996
MARY!

29:33.840 --> 29:35.831
Man: OHH!

29:35.870 --> 29:37.667
Mary: [ PANTING ]

29:37.700 --> 29:39.634
Titu ba: MARY!

29:39.670 --> 29:41.069
Mary: [ GASPS ]

29:41.110 --> 29:42.475
Titu ba: MARY!
MARY!

29:42.510 --> 29:44.239
MARY, COME OUT NOW!

29:44.280 --> 29:46.578
MARY!
MARY, COME OUT NOW!

29:46.610 --> 29:48.419
MARY! MARY, COME OUT NOW!

29:48.450 --> 29:49.849
Mary: [ GASPS ]

29:49.880 --> 29:50.812
Tituba: OH, MARY.

29:50.850 --> 29:52.317
Mary: OH, TITUBA.

29:52.350 --> 29:54.284
Tituba: IT'S OKAY.
YOU'RE HOME.

29:54.320 --> 29:56.185
WHY DID YOU GO BACK?

29:56.220 --> 29:58.654
I TOLD YOU NOT TO GO BACK.

29:58.690 --> 30:01.420
AND YOU LEFI' THIS ONE TO WALK
ALONE ON HER FIRST TIME.

30:01.460 --> 30:02.859
ANYTHING COULD HAVE HAPPENED.

30:02.900 --> 30:04.367
Mary:
I KNOW. I'M SORRY.

30:04.400 --> 30:06.368
I JUST WANTED TO SEE HIM AGAIN.

30:06.400 --> 30:08.664
I LOST CONTROL.

30:08.700 --> 30:11.601
Tituba:
YOU GET YOUR CLOTHES ON.

30:11.640 --> 30:12.834
YOU'RE COMING TO HELP ME.

30:12.870 --> 30:14.178
Mary: NO, NO.
WHERE ARE YOU GOING?

30:14.210 --> 30:15.939
Tituba: SHH.
TO FETCH YOU AN APPLE

30:15.980 --> 30:17.538
WHILE YOU REGAIN YOUR CONTROL.

30:17.580 --> 30:21.971
Mary: [ PANTING ]

30:22.020 --> 30:23.840
Tituba: IT'S OKAY.

30:51.250 --> 30:53.878
John: MM!

31:02.090 --> 31:03.853
[ BOTH PANTING ]

31:23.440 --> 31:25.203
[ INSECTS CHIRPING ]

31:29.220 --> 31:31.142
Tituba:
HAND IT TO ME, GIRL.

31:42.630 --> 31:44.928
Man: SHE'S DEAD!

31:44.970 --> 31:47.427
LADY TRASK IS DEAD!

31:47.470 --> 31:51.634
[ MEN SHOUTING IN DISTANCE ]

31:51.670 --> 31:53.160
Tituba: WHAT DID YOU DO?

31:55.180 --> 31:57.307
Mercy:
WHAT MARY TOLD ME TO DO.

31:57.340 --> 32:00.309
Tituba: SHE TOLD YOU TO FRIGHTEN
THE WOMAN, NOT SLAUGHTER HER.

32:00.350 --> 32:01.669
Mercy:
BUT SHE DESERVED IT.

32:03.820 --> 32:06.243
WE'RE TIRED.

32:06.290 --> 32:09.782
TIRED OF BEING BEATEN AND USED.

32:09.820 --> 32:13.381
WE WON'T BE USED ANYMORE --
ANY OF US.

32:13.430 --> 32:15.295
WE WON'T TAKE IT.

32:17.200 --> 32:19.498
Man:
MAKE WAY! MAKE WAY!

32:19.530 --> 32:20.599
[ INDISTINCT SHOUTING ]

32:27.470 --> 32:30.177
Cotton: ISAAC!
ISAAC, WHAT'S HAPPENED?

32:30.210 --> 32:33.509
Isaac: MRS. TRASK HAS BEEN FOUND
DEAD -- HORRIBLY DEAD.

32:33.550 --> 32:35.916
AND THEY ALL THINK THE BARKERS
ARE RESPONSIBLE.

32:35.950 --> 32:37.815
AFTER THE FIGHT
AND WHAT LITTLE DOLLIE SAW,

32:37.850 --> 32:39.511
NOW THIS,
THEY'RE CALLING THEM WITCHES.

32:39.550 --> 32:40.949
Cotton:
WHERE IS CAPTAIN ALDEN?

32:40.990 --> 32:42.548
Isaac:
HE IS NOWHERE TO BE FOUND.

32:44.230 --> 32:45.629
Cotton: PEOPLE, WAIT!

32:45.660 --> 32:47.184
WAIT!
WHAT ARE YOU DOING?!

32:47.230 --> 32:48.857
Woman:
THOSE DAMNED BARKERS!

32:48.900 --> 32:50.527
THEY'VE CURSED TOO MANY OF US.

32:50.560 --> 32:51.868
Cotton:
WHAT HAVE THEY DONE?!

32:51.900 --> 32:53.322
Man: ROTTED ALL OUR WINTER
SUPPLY OF GRAIN!

32:53.370 --> 32:54.837
Woman:
SHE KILLED GOODY TRASK!

32:54.870 --> 32:58.704
Cotton: PROOF?!
HAVE ANY OF YOU ANY PROOF?!

32:58.740 --> 33:00.367
Man:
MAKE WAY! YOU THERE!

33:00.410 --> 33:01.968
Cotton: THE WHOLE TOWN
HAS GONE MAD!

33:02.010 --> 33:03.375
WE HAVE GOT TO STOP THEM!

33:03.410 --> 33:05.173
Mr. Hale: NOTHING MORE DANGEROUS
THAN A MOB.

33:05.210 --> 33:06.802
BEST NOT TO INTERVENE.

33:06.850 --> 33:09.171
Cotton: YOU ARE MAGISTRATE.
YOU REPRESENT THE LAW.

33:09.220 --> 33:12.189
Mr. Hale: THE LAW'S MEANINGLESS
WITHOUT SUPPORT OF THE PEOPLE.

33:16.690 --> 33:19.329
Cotton: FRIENDS!
NEIGHBORS!

33:19.360 --> 33:21.191
PEOPLE OF SALEM, STOP!

33:21.230 --> 33:23.391
THINK WHAT YOU DO!

33:23.430 --> 33:25.227
Man:
YOU KNOW THERE ARE WITCHES!

33:25.270 --> 33:26.328
YOU'VE TOLD US SO!

33:26.370 --> 33:29.362
AND HERE BE THREE OF THEM!

33:29.400 --> 33:30.867
WHAT WILL YOU DO WITH THEM?!

33:30.900 --> 33:32.709
Cotton: IF THEY BE WITCHES,
WE WILL FIND OUT.

33:32.740 --> 33:34.708
BUT THIS IS NOT THE WAY!

33:34.740 --> 33:35.934
Woman: WOULD YOU JUST
LET THEM GO?

33:38.910 --> 33:40.502
Cotton: NO.

33:40.550 --> 33:43.246
NO, WE PUT THEM IN THE JAIL!

33:43.280 --> 33:46.738
WE HOLD THEM FOR THE NIGHT
WHILE PASSIONS COOL.

33:46.790 --> 33:49.384
AND THEN IN THE CLEAR LIGHT
OF DAY,

33:49.420 --> 33:52.355
WE WILL EXAMINE THEM
AS THE LAW ALLOWS!

33:52.390 --> 33:55.427
EVERY ONE OF US HAS THE RIGHT
TO DEFEND OURSELVES,

33:55.460 --> 33:57.052
TO RESPOND TO OUR ACCUSERS!

33:57.100 --> 34:00.228
Woman: MRS. TRASK IS DEAD,
SLAUGHTERED LIKE A LAMB!

34:00.270 --> 34:01.862
Cotton: TRUE.

34:01.900 --> 34:04.107
EVIL HAS BEEN DONE
THIS NIGHT ALREADY.

34:04.140 --> 34:07.166
BUT DO NOT COMPOUND IT
BY DOING MORE.

34:07.210 --> 34:12.147
DO NOT RUSH TO DO
WHAT CAN NEVER BE UNDONE.

34:13.910 --> 34:15.514
IF THEY BE GUILTY NOW,

34:15.550 --> 34:18.587
THEY WILL BE JUST AS GUILTY
IN THE MORNING.

34:20.490 --> 34:23.550
AFTER A FAIR TRIAL.

34:26.390 --> 34:29.928
Mr. Hale: QUITE RIGHT.
MEN, TAKE THEM TO THE JAIL.

34:29.960 --> 34:35.592
Woman: WITCHES! MURDERERS!
MURDERERS!

34:35.640 --> 34:37.892
MURDERERS!

34:37.940 --> 34:39.828
[ INDISTINCT SHOUTING ]

34:47.350 --> 34:48.942
Gloriana: COTTON, I THINK

34:48.980 --> 34:51.744
THAT WAS THE BRAVEST THING
I'VE EVER SEEN.

34:51.790 --> 34:55.487
LIKE WATCHING A MAN STICK HIS
HEAD INSIDE OF A LION'S JAWS.

34:56.660 --> 34:58.719
I WOULD REWARD YOU
FOR YOUR BRAVERY.

34:58.760 --> 35:00.625
Cotton:
I WOULD GLADLY ACCEPT IT,

35:00.660 --> 35:02.992
BUT NOW IS NOT THE TIME.

35:03.030 --> 35:07.319
I CANNOT DENY MY FEELINGS.
THEY ARE REAL.

35:07.370 --> 35:10.828
BUT I DO NOT WANT ANY LONGER
TO BE YOUR CUSTOMER.

35:10.870 --> 35:14.408
DO YOU UNDERSTAND?

35:14.440 --> 35:16.374
Gloriana: I THINK SO.

35:17.840 --> 35:20.479
WILL I EVER SEE YOU AGAIN?

35:20.510 --> 35:21.670
Cotton: YES.

35:21.720 --> 35:23.574
BUT YOU MUST LEAVE ME NOW...

35:23.620 --> 35:26.088
TILL I SORT THINGS OUT.

35:26.120 --> 35:29.988
WHEN I DO,
EVERYTHING WILL BE DIFFERENT.

35:30.020 --> 35:32.181
I PROMISE.

35:36.200 --> 35:38.225
[ FOOTSTEPS APPROACHING ]

36:22.380 --> 36:24.371
Mary: WAIT.

36:24.410 --> 36:27.573
John: SEVEN YEARS IS
A LONG ENOUGH TIME TO WAIT.

36:27.610 --> 36:29.248
MM.

36:32.420 --> 36:35.082
Mary: STOP.

36:35.120 --> 36:37.714
John: MARY.

36:37.760 --> 36:40.354
I KNOW YOU'VE DREAMT OF THIS.

36:40.390 --> 36:42.858
WHEN IT COMES TO DREAMS,
YOU ONLY GOT ONE CHOICE.

36:42.900 --> 36:45.721
YOU FORGET THEM...

36:45.770 --> 36:49.160
OR YOU LIVE THEM.

36:49.200 --> 36:52.203
AND I'M DONE
TRYING TO FORGET THEM.

36:56.140 --> 36:58.904
Mary: AND WHAT IF
IN LIVING OUR DREAMS

36:58.950 --> 37:01.168
THEY BECOME NIGHTMARES?

37:01.210 --> 37:03.815
John: ALL THAT MATTERS
IS YOU AND ME.

37:07.390 --> 37:11.258
Mary: YOU ALWAYS MAKE EVERYTHING
SOUND SO SIMPLE.

37:17.660 --> 37:20.925
John: YOU DON'T HAVE
ANY CHILDREN WITH SIBLEY.

37:20.970 --> 37:23.359
YOU CAN'T CARE ABOUT HIM.

37:23.400 --> 37:25.106
YOU HAVEN'T CARED

37:25.140 --> 37:27.563
ABOUT WHAT OTHER PEOPLE HAVE
THOUGHT BEFORE, SO FOR ONCE...

37:30.440 --> 37:33.079
...LET'S JUST LIVE FOR US.

37:35.280 --> 37:38.408
Mary:
I WISH IT WERE POSSIBLE.

37:38.450 --> 37:41.613
John:
AND WHY ISN'T IT?

37:41.660 --> 37:43.855
Mary: IT JUST ISN'T.

37:46.660 --> 37:48.127
I WANT YOU TO LEAVE.

37:51.000 --> 37:52.661
John: NO.

37:52.700 --> 37:57.797
Mary: I'VE GOTTEN ALL I NEEDED
FROM YOU.

37:57.840 --> 38:00.035
PLEASE LEAVE.

38:06.480 --> 38:08.004
John:
WHAT HAPPENED TO YOU?

38:10.650 --> 38:12.618
WHAT ARE YOU NOT TELLING ME?

38:12.650 --> 38:14.686
BECAUSE THIS MAKES NO SENSE.

38:27.870 --> 38:29.360
WELL...

38:31.370 --> 38:34.407
...I'M HAPPY TO HAVE BEEN
OF SERVICE.

38:48.420 --> 38:49.751
Mary: [ SOBS ]

38:53.230 --> 38:54.822
[ MEN SHOUTING IN DISTANCE ]

38:54.860 --> 38:57.192
Cotton: [ SNIFFING ]

38:58.830 --> 39:00.821
WHAT IS IT?!
WHAT'S BURNING?!

39:00.870 --> 39:03.964
Isaac: THE BARKERS!
ALL OF THEM BURNED AS WITCHES!

39:04.000 --> 39:04.830
Cotton: WHAT?!

39:04.870 --> 39:06.838
BY WHOSE AUTHORITY?!

39:06.870 --> 39:08.235
Grim Man: MINE.

39:11.410 --> 39:13.207
Cotton: FATHER.

39:13.250 --> 39:17.573
Increase: I SEE I'VE INDULGED
YOUR JUVENILE CURIOSITY

39:17.620 --> 39:20.088
FAR, FAR TOO MUCH.

39:20.120 --> 39:21.348
TSK, TSK, TSK.

39:21.390 --> 39:23.210
LOOK AT YOU.

39:23.260 --> 39:28.027
SURROUNDING YOURSELF WITH ALL
THESE FEEBLE TOOLS OF REASON.

39:28.060 --> 39:30.551
Cotton: BUT, FATHER,
THEY MIGHT HAVE BEEN INNOCENT.

39:30.600 --> 39:32.261
Increase: IN NOCENT?

39:32.300 --> 39:34.063
INNOCENT OF WHAT?

39:34.100 --> 39:37.536
THE FAMILY IS WELL-KNOWN
AS WASTRELS AND CURS.

39:37.570 --> 39:39.367
Cotton: THEY HAD NO TRIAL,
NO EXAMINATION.

39:39.410 --> 39:41.366
Increase: AND THEY SHALL RECEIVE
THEIR TRIAL

39:41.410 --> 39:43.571
BEFORE THE GREATEST
AND MOST MERCIFUL OF JUDGES.

39:43.610 --> 39:46.340
[ BARKERS SCREAMING ]

39:46.380 --> 39:49.213
AND IF THEY ARE DEEMED
TO BE INNOCENT,

39:49.250 --> 39:52.378
I TRUST THE LORD WILL SEE
TO THEIR RECOMPENSE.

39:52.420 --> 39:55.184
BUT YOU...

39:55.220 --> 39:58.553
YOU -- HAVE YOU TURNED IMBECILE?

39:58.590 --> 40:03.550
ALL YOU DO IS SOW
THE DEADLY SEEDS OF DOUBT.

40:03.600 --> 40:06.228
DO YOU NOT SEE,

40:06.270 --> 40:08.761
WHEN HUNTING WITCHES,

40:08.800 --> 40:11.064
FAR BETTER A HUNDRED
INNOCENTS DIE

40:11.100 --> 40:15.230
THAN A SINGLE SOLITARY WITCH
WALKS FREE?

40:15.280 --> 40:16.838
YES!

40:18.750 --> 40:21.446
NOW, SIT YOU DOWN.

40:21.480 --> 40:25.280
CONSIDER YOUR MISTAKES.

40:25.320 --> 40:28.653
SIT.

40:50.940 --> 40:52.908
[ CHUCKLES ]

40:52.950 --> 40:55.976
Cotton:
WHERE ARE YOU GOING?

40:56.020 --> 40:58.716
THERE'S NO ONE LEFT TO BURN
AT THIS HOUR.

41:01.350 --> 41:05.127
Increase:
WATCH YOUR TONGUE, BOY.

41:05.160 --> 41:10.325
YOU THINK YOU'RE TOO OLD TO BE
WHIPPED BY YOUR FATHER, HMM?

41:16.470 --> 41:17.994
HUH?

41:25.310 --> 41:28.245
[ INSECTS CHIRPING ]

41:39.760 --> 41:43.526
Isaac: YOU'RE TOO LATE.

41:43.560 --> 41:46.723
I THOUGHT YOU WERE GOING
TO SAVE US.

41:49.000 --> 41:52.868
BUT MAYBE WE JUST DON'T
DESERVE SAVING.

42:01.550 --> 42:07.238
Increase: IT'S A PRETTY PIECE
OF PAGANISM, I'LL GRANT YOU.

42:07.290 --> 42:11.727
BUT NOT FIT FOR PUBLIC VIEWING.

42:11.760 --> 42:16.390
Mary: THAT IS WHY
IT ENLIGHTENS MY BEDROOM,

42:16.430 --> 42:20.389
WHERE ONLY MY NEAREST
AND DEAREST ARE ALLOWED.

42:20.430 --> 42:24.434
LIKE YOU, MY DEAR INCREASE.

42:24.470 --> 42:27.564
I CAN'T TELL YOU WHAT IT MEANS
TO SEE YOU.

42:27.610 --> 42:30.204
HOW WAS LONDON
AND THE KING'S COURT?

42:30.240 --> 42:32.902
Increase:
CORRUPT, AS ALWAYS.

42:32.950 --> 42:37.444
THE KING HAS GRANTED US
A NEW CHARTER,

42:37.480 --> 42:41.382
FULL CLAIM ON THIS CHOSEN LAND
OF OURS,

42:41.420 --> 42:44.856
AND HE PROMISES A NEW GOVERNOR
IN THE SPRING,

42:44.890 --> 42:46.949
A MAN EXPERIENCED IN WARFARE,

42:46.990 --> 42:50.198
TO HELP US PURGE AND ERADICATE
THE HEATHEN SAVAGES

42:50.230 --> 42:53.358
IN OUR MIDST
FOR NOW AND FOREVER.

42:53.400 --> 42:55.561
Mary: WHAT A TREMENDOUS VICTORY
FOR YOU.

42:55.600 --> 42:56.430
FOR ALL OF US.

42:56.470 --> 42:58.028
Increase: INDEED.

42:58.070 --> 43:01.233
WHEN I SET SAIL FOR HOME,
I WAS FULL OF ELATION.

43:01.270 --> 43:03.909
I COULD HAVE SAILED
ON MY HOPES ALONE.

43:03.940 --> 43:06.579
I SHOULD HAVE KNOWN
THAT THE FORCES OF EVIL

43:06.610 --> 43:09.272
WOULD TRY TO HINDER ME.

43:09.320 --> 43:12.084
Mary: WHO?
AGENTS OF THE FRENCH?

43:12.120 --> 43:14.418
Increase: WITCHES.

43:14.450 --> 43:17.089
OF COURSE,
THEY DID ALL THEY COULD.

43:17.120 --> 43:19.759
THEY STILLED THE WINDS
AND TRAPPED THE SHIP.

43:19.790 --> 43:23.954
THEY SPREAD DISEASE AND DISSENT
ALL AROUND.

43:24.000 --> 43:26.423
MANY DIED.

43:26.470 --> 43:28.597
BUT THEY DID NOT DIE IN VAIN.

43:28.640 --> 43:31.097
Mary:
PRAISE GOD YOU MADE IT

43:31.140 --> 43:35.770
AND LANDED SAFELY ON OUR SHORES
TO LIGHTEN OUR BENIGHTED TOWN,

43:35.810 --> 43:39.302
LIKE THE SUN RETURNING
AFTER THE DARKEST OF NIGHTS.

43:39.350 --> 43:41.306
Increase: MARY SIBLEY,

43:41.350 --> 43:44.649
HOWEVER DARK THE NIGHT,

43:44.690 --> 43:50.117
YOUR EYES STILL SHINE
SO BRIGHTLY.

43:50.160 --> 43:54.153
YOU KNOW, I DO BELIEVE
MY GOOD FRIEND GEORGE,

43:54.190 --> 43:58.627
FOR ALL HIS SUFFERING,
IS THE LUCKIEST MAN IN SALEM.

43:58.670 --> 44:02.993
AND SPEAKING OF MY FRIEND,
I SHOULD LIKE TO SEE HIM.

44:03.040 --> 44:04.291
MAY I?

44:04.340 --> 44:05.830
Mary:
HE IS PARTICULARLY UNWELL.

44:05.870 --> 44:07.633
THANKFULLY,
HE'S RESTING AT PRESENT.

44:07.670 --> 44:08.807
Increase: AH.

44:08.840 --> 44:10.102
Mary:
YOU MUST RETURN TOMORROW.

44:10.140 --> 44:11.801
I'M SURE THE VERY SIGHT OF YOU

44:11.850 --> 44:14.341
WILL CHEER HIM IMMENSELY,
AS IT HAS ME.

44:14.380 --> 44:17.019
YOUR PRESENCE IN SALEM
CAN ONLY BE A TONIC

44:17.050 --> 44:20.178
FOR ALL OF US
IN THESE DARK TIMES.

44:26.860 --> 44:31.354
HOW LONG MAY WE ENJOY YOUR
CURATIVE PRESENCE IN TOWN?

44:31.400 --> 44:33.368
Increase: WHY...

44:35.700 --> 44:39.363
...UNTIL EVERY LAST
DEVIL'S WHORE OF A WITCH

44:39.410 --> 44:41.970
IN SALEM IS DEAD.

44:50.520 --> 44:53.546
-- Captions by VITAC --
